### =========================================================
### Product Query APIs
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN
@passportId = 019cbc97-fa07-7072-b36b-efee059e1af5

### 1) Get Passport Detail (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}

### 2) Get Asset State (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/state

### 3) Get Current Owner (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/owner

### 4) List My Passports
### Scope: isAuthenticated()
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/me/passports
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
